{"tid":681303,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"額頭有台灣刺青   英男慘遭中國人群毆","createTime":"2018-05-28T02:23:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-28T10:19:29.000Z","uid":184679,"like":179,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":59,"replies":[{"pid":"0a0f7fa3375a7b448b775d4ad397e665ad6d0684","tid":681303,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T02:23:21.000Z","msg":"一名英國男子在柬埔寨遭到十幾名中國男子毆打，只因為他的額頭上有「臺灣」刺青。<br />\n<br />\n台灣英文新聞（Taiwan News）27日報導，英國籍男子保羅（Paul，中文姓名為羅翰）在台灣生活10多年，日前到柬埔寨度假。在當地時間5月26日晚上11點左右到西哈努克維爾市（Sihanoukville）的一個酒吧。<br />\n<br />\n當他坐下來脫了帽子後，大約十多名中國男子圍了過來，因為看到他額頭上的「臺灣」刺青。其中一名中國男子喊道：「中國的台灣！」保羅回應說：「台灣，台灣！」<br />\n<br />\n「接著這群中國男子像瘋了一樣，拿起棍子開始攻擊我。」保羅說，「並強迫我說台灣是中國的一部分。」<br />\n<br />\n遭到群毆的保羅，頭部及身體有多處瘀傷，嘴唇腫脹，掉了兩顆牙齒，嘴巴無法閉合。他事後在臉書上提醒台灣人到柬埔寨旅行時要小心。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.epochtimes.com/assets/uploads/2018/05/20180527_TWN-600x340.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.epochtimes.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F05%2F20180527_TWN-600x340.jpg&h=45baacb2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n來台10多年的保羅，定居在高雄鹽埕區，娶台灣老婆，在台灣開酒吧。台灣多家媒體去年10月報導保羅在額頭上及下巴刺上台灣二字及地圖。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.epochtimes.com/b5/18/5/27/n10431750.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.epochtimes.com%2Fb5%2F18%2F5%2F27%2Fn10431750.htm&d=svrvB11%2FOjkRJrQQYRknZzCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=44662d92\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.epochtimes.com/b5/18/5/27/n10431750.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79f8521de603d50ab7efee6e815e835f9a54b3d0","tid":681303,"uid":184679,"like":101,"dislike":1,"score":100,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T02:25:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">British man beaten by 10 Chinese in Cambodia for having 'Taiwan' tattooed on his forehead</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://tnimage.taiwannews.com.tw/photos/shares/5b0a913f9b466.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftnimage.taiwannews.com.tw%2Fphotos%2Fshares%2F5b0a913f9b466.jpg&h=4cbd9519&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91095a10ca1e91fe9607c268f2d26d758da1bd46","tid":681303,"uid":60137,"like":251,"dislike":5,"score":246,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T02:26:49.000Z","msg":"支那豬即係支那豬，無撚文化又野蠻，留半個係世上都嫌多"},{"pid":"b4d34c0a493781200146413403b85ea38d11ff7a","tid":681303,"uid":2419,"like":40,"dislike":0,"score":40,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T02:28:25.000Z","msg":"taiwan no.1"},{"pid":"3ff1854b2eff12dcb887c9dc93f250a4ad119351","tid":681303,"uid":185683,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T02:31:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fed5af8ecbc5392f47534b34f27e23113d56a4b4","tid":681303,"uid":45788,"like":50,"dislike":0,"score":50,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T02:33:26.000Z","msg":"去外國都要小心被玻璃碎整到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af99bedc16a53ca1c77d1d638f4fe58dc2c9899d","tid":681303,"uid":132859,"like":39,"dislike":1,"score":38,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T02:34:23.000Z","msg":"新一代紅衛兵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d471e8d60161a52f1d7338d1881f0d5cf511860","tid":681303,"uid":164913,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T02:35:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1e7d9425bc0c59fdf22e5c9659b61cb73fc9b02e","tid":681303,"uid":113626,"like":9,"dislike":12,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T02:36:56.000Z","msg":"又一次證明白人係世界第一<br />\n低端人口要圍爐十打一先打得贏到個正常人"},{"pid":"0b1c9048e2851400eab6d215da32e1711b49de8f","tid":681303,"uid":160662,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"6d471e8d60161a52f1d7338d1881f0d5cf511860","tid":681303,"uid":164913,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T02:35:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T02:36:59.000Z","msg":"圖一係PS過啫應該<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2875a70c457375f85fd7ca915f4f486e2062f442","tid":681303,"uid":26333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T02:44:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"749e687d12f99abafc58e9d9c12a109272f51a2a","tid":681303,"uid":131569,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T02:52:02.000Z","msg":"同一種族就要under同一個政權<br />\n根本同納綷黨無分別。"},{"pid":"9247dbbd2339a087771dedc927f51ae050ab3a33","tid":681303,"uid":53379,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T02:56:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180528/s00005/6bb40967ca5355607f02f8dafe9bf7b2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180528%2Fs00005%2F6bb40967ca5355607f02f8dafe9bf7b2.jpg&h=acfae3ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在台灣居住14年的英國男子羅翰，去年醉酒時在自己額頭紋上「台灣」刺青，該紋身使他近日在柬埔寨旅遊時，引起多名中國人不滿。羅翰因拒絕承認台灣是中國的一部分，遭10多人圍毆，他的臉部被打至紅腫流血。<br />\n<br />\n事發周一（27日），羅翰在柬埔寨一間酒吧落單後脫下帽子，附近一群中國男子看見他前額的「台灣」紋身，其中一人說「Taiwan，China（中國台灣）」羅翰聽後反駁「Taiwan，Taiwan（台灣台灣）」結果遭至少10人衝上前圍毆，要求他承認台灣是中國的。<br />\n<br />\n羅翰拒認台灣屬於中國，但考慮到自己的人身安全，只好妥協「你認為台灣是中國的，我便會說台灣是中國的，我只想離開。」<br />\n<br />\n遭毆打後，羅翰的頭部、身體多處瘀傷，嘴唇腫起、2顆牙齒被打落。他形容這是一次痛心的遭遇，指以後自己在外面不敢脫下帽子了，同時會設法清除前額的紋身，直言它是一個「愚蠢的醉酒錯誤」。羅翰又提醒台灣人到海外要注意安全，「雖然有很多中國人很好，但顯然我遇到一群不太好」。<br />\n<br />\n羅翰20歲時與台灣女友結婚後定居高雄，在當地經營一間英式酒吧，目前已入籍台灣公民。他因去年10月在醉酒後在額頭紋上「台灣」、下巴刺「台灣旗」圖樣引起關注。<br />\n<br />\n（台灣英文新聞／EToday新聞雲）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180528/s00005/1527471416701\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180528%2Fs00005%2F1527471416701&d=svrvB11%2FOjkRJrQQYRknZzCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=a6188602\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180528%2Fs00005%2F1527471416701&h=d3063973\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180528/s00005/1527471416701</a>"},{"pid":"c344ebbcde3fc83200cf0bdc63a9541bc0a04241","tid":681303,"uid":131157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T03:01:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c442b0548d7a416f52c3e769a7a58f3524742fb2","tid":681303,"uid":154725,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T03:02:39.000Z","msg":"瘋了 全都瘋了"},{"pid":"4ffd47da543329bfb86dd400907e2659c059ea9a","tid":681303,"uid":3454,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"c442b0548d7a416f52c3e769a7a58f3524742fb2","tid":681303,"uid":154725,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T03:02:39.000Z","msg":"瘋了 全都瘋了"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T03:23:33.000Z","msg":"往死裡打"},{"pid":"912e32b177834afbfed665ce615c6efd45148fd1","tid":681303,"uid":6752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T03:25:44.000Z","msg":"冇後續班支那狗點？"},{"pid":"653db4d612699439cd9016c46825ec7093dbf5be","tid":681303,"uid":281,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T03:26:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7cbd537d67911e19f61159d29c648aeaa5c2944d","tid":681303,"uid":53672,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T03:29:46.000Z","msg":"好心班生番咁愛國就唔好出國啦，下下講手，成個黃種人條線比佢班垃圾拉低哂"},{"pid":"2a1e68409d168f301e62848d719afbdad7a6335a","tid":681303,"uid":63154,"like":12,"dislike":2,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T03:32:50.000Z","msg":"生番即係生番，台灣可以上Facebook同youtube架，食屎啦支那豬"},{"pid":"36cc0385b5457c53b45b41f8a45f4a2ee21e4c18","tid":681303,"uid":71467,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T04:04:01.000Z","msg":"好撚慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c553e4fa4863812ebcff7e56f6e2f32b272c111","tid":681303,"uid":3457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"912e32b177834afbfed665ce615c6efd45148fd1","tid":681303,"uid":6752,"like":0,"dislik